{"tid":1924704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國外交部發言人稱美軍或把病毒傳武漢   美國務院召見中國大使表抗議","createTime":"2020-03-13T23:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T16:59:43.000Z","uid":141151,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"280624e0cbf1831cbb2ba94e7e2ccaa70cf0526a","tid":1924704,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T23:17:24.000Z","msg":"中國外交部發言人稱美軍或把病毒傳武漢<br />\n美國務院召見中國大使表抗議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-china-cui-tiankai-summoned-for-coronavirus-conspiracy-allegations-20200313/5328199.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fus-china-cui-tiankai-summoned-for-coronavirus-conspiracy-allegations-20200313%2F5328199.html&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=83187993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-china-cui-tiankai-summoned-for-coronavirus-conspiracy-allegations-20200313/5328199.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院星期五(3月13日)召見中國駐美國大使崔天凱，就中國外交部發言人趙立堅有關美國政府隱瞞疫情真相而且新冠病毒有可能由美軍帶到武漢的說法表示抗議。<br />\n<br />\n路透社援引一位不透露姓名的美國國務院官員的話說：&ldquo;他就中國外交部發言人有關新冠病毒的言論被召見。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n中國駐華盛頓使館暫時還沒有發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅星期四在他的推特賬戶指責美國政府隱瞞真相，要求美方解釋，並說病毒可能是美軍帶到武漢。推特在中國是禁用的。<br />\n<br />\n星期五，中國外交部發言人耿爽在記者會上沒有正面回答他的同事趙立堅提出的指稱。耿爽說：&ldquo;中方始終認為，這是一個科學問題，需要聽取科學和專業的意見。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a5a52598d6cab17f3fa547a1513cd030cf84408f","tid":1924704,"uid":271894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T23:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驅逐出境"},{"pid":"710f151f562893b6bf4d71140dd64676f7a1a9f1","tid":1924704,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T23:25:25.000Z","msg":"捉